content: JhChoy: Fixed three bugs this month, merging PRs #2789, #2788, and #2802 that addressed issues with Twitter timeline name parsing, topics formatting in compose state, and single quote handling in JSON array parsing. The most substantial change was PR #2802, which involved significant code modifications (+13034/-2573 lines), though there appears to be a discrepancy between the PR description (+26/-5 lines) and the actual changes. Activity was sporadic, with contributions on only 2 days this month, primarily focused on bugfix work (80%).
